# pedal-bench backend env vars.
#
# Optional. Required only for the AI-powered features:
#   - BOM extraction fallback for older PedalPCB PDFs (Parts List layout)
#   - Drill-template extraction fallback for image-only / unusual PDFs
#   - Component photo verification (BOM tab → "verify" button)
#   - AI diagnosis (Debug tab)
#
# Modern PedalPCB PDFs ingest fully without this key — only the
# AI-specific features need it.
#
# Two ways to provide a key:
#   1. SELF-HOST: set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY here. Loaded at backend startup.
#   2. BYOK (any user): paste the key into Settings in the web UI.
#      It's stored in browser localStorage and sent as a request header.
#      Never persists server-side.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Set a usage limit at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/limits
# (recommended: $20/month while you're getting a feel for it).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
